---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="关于 - Edward 的博客">
  <section class="py-16 pb-10">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 font-mono text-[11.5px] text-stone-500 mb-5.5">
      <span>关于我</span>
    </div>
    
    <h1 class="font-sans text-[34px] leading-[1.18] tracking-tight font-semibold mb-4.5 text-stone-900">
      关于
    </h1>
  </section>

  <section class="pt-9 pb-7 border-t border-stone-200 prose prose-stone max-w-none">
    <div class="text-stone-700 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
      <p>
        你好！我是 Edward，一名个人开发者、AI 爱好者和技术写作者。
      </p>
      
      <p>
        我喜欢构建有趣的东西，探索人工智能的可能性，并分享我的学习旅程。这个博客是我记录技术笔记、项目展示和思考的地方。
      </p>

      <h3 class="font-mono text-sm font-medium text-stone-900 mt-6 mb-3">// 技术栈</h3>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <span class="font-mono text-[11px] text-stone-500 border border-stone-200 px-2 py-1 rounded">TypeScript</span>
        <span class="font-mono text-[11px] text-stone-500 border border-stone-200 px-2 py-1 rounded">Python</span>
        <span class="font-mono text-[11px] text-stone-500 border border-stone-200 px-2 py-1 rounded">Rust</span>
        <span class="font-mono text-[11px] text-stone-500 border border-stone-200 px-2 py-1 rounded">Astro</span>
        <span class="font-mono text-[11px] text-stone-500 border border-stone-200 px-2 py-1 rounded">Docker</span>
        <span class="font-mono text-[11px] text-stone-500 border border-stone-200 px-2 py-1 rounded">Kubernetes</span>
        <span class="font-mono text-[11px] text-stone-500 border border-stone-200 px-2 py-1 rounded">AI/ML</span>
      </div>

      <h3 class="font-mono text-sm font-medium text-stone-900 mt-6 mb-3">// 联系方式</h3>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 font-mono text-[12.5px]">
        <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-stone-700 hover:text-orange-600 border-b border-dashed border-stone-300 hover:border-orange-600 pb-0.5 transition-colors">GitHub</a>
        <a href="https://twitter.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-stone-700 hover:text-orange-600 border-b border-dashed border-stone-300 hover:border-orange-600 pb-0.5 transition-colors">Twitter</a>
        <a href="mailto:hello@example.com" class="text-stone-700 hover:text-orange-600 border-b border-dashed border-stone-300 hover:border-orange-600 pb-0.5 transition-colors">Email</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
